          checkResult added;
          MDP Broker:
          Many brokers in one process.

  .

  [0.1.0] Major Review:
          Conduits replace enumerators,
          Interfaces simplified to ByteString,
          Interfaces simplified in general,
          Advanced patterns:
          Majordomo Broker.

  .

  [0.0.1] Initial Release.

